WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.149
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:03.159 --> 00:00:05.190
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.749
We're excited to be here.

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:09.790
Well, praise the Lord. Yes,

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:11.749
we're here to work

00:00:11.759 --> 00:00:15.070
it;

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:17.230
we have work to do,

00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:21.790
a path to clear, a road to lay.

00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:23.790
Everything is so important in the spirit

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:27.470
realm right now. I have such an urgency;

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:27.480
Diana

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:30.910
and I both do. I want

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.870
you to visualize what he was saying

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:36.270
yesterday: acting like it's already

00:00:36.280 --> 00:00:40.549
done. For your miracle, what

00:00:40.559 --> 00:00:41.750
would you

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:45.229
do if you got what you're believing for

00:00:45.239 --> 00:00:48.670
in the next five minutes? If you knew the

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:51.069
breakthrough

00:00:51.079 --> 00:00:53.830
was coming through in the next five

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:56.430
minutes and you could set

00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:57.990
your timer on it,

00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.509
what would you do? How would

00:00:59.519 --> 00:01:00.630
you act?

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:03.029
In

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:06.950
just that split second he

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:09.070
downloaded that to me yesterday, he said,

00:01:09.080 --> 00:01:12.149
'Act like you've already got it.'Let your

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:15.749
praise, like Brother Hagin said, let your

00:01:15.759 --> 00:01:18.590
praises

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:22.190
equal your

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:24.710
prayers. If you're praying a lot about it,

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.950
let it be

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:29.310
like a scale in the spirit realm. Let

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:33.510
your praises elevate and go up

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:35.310
as much as you're praying about it.

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:39.030
Praise, prayer; praise, prayer. So that

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:41.429
you're glorifying God and you're

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:43.429
praying, but you're

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:46.149
taking the care out of your prayer.

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:48.670
We're not begging believers; we're

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:51.550
believing believers that

00:01:51.560 --> 00:01:54.109
realize the

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:56.230
manifestation is coming. We're not trying

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:59.510
to persuade God to give us something: 'God,

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:01.749
please, please bring my

00:02:01.749 --> 00:02:01.759
miracle.'No,

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:05.190
thank you. I'm taking the care

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:08.229
and the worry. 'Oh God, they gave

00:02:08.239 --> 00:02:10.869
me a bad report. Oh God, they told me that

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:12.670
they're going to come and repo our car

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:14.070
tomorrow, or I

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:16.869
don't have enough money tomorrow. Lord,

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:20.589
the light bill is due and I need

00:02:20.589 --> 00:02:20.599
a

00:02:20.599 --> 00:02:22.790
new pair of

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.390
shoes.'You've

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:26.790
got all this care because of

00:02:26.790 --> 00:02:26.800
the

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:29.509
deadline, the pressure of time. Bending to the pressure of

00:02:29.519 --> 00:02:31.830
time—the

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:34.670
pressure is always on you.

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:37.710
The bills are always due, the

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:40.390
kids need food, the kids need new

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:43.030
shoes, new clothes, the

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.229
school is wanting some kind of field

00:02:45.239 --> 00:02:47.350
trip. You've got a

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.309
need, but the

00:02:50.319 --> 00:02:52.830
care of the world weighs on our

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:56.990
shoulders. It's

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.270
just human nature. But read that

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:02.990
scripture: 'Be careful for nothing, but in

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:05.190
everything by prayer and supplication

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:07.509
with thanksgiving, let your requests be

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:10.149
made known unto

00:03:10.149 --> 00:03:10.159
God.'So

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:14.350
with thanksgiving, yes.

00:03:16.480 --> 00:03:18.550
That's what he was telling me: act like

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:21.509
you've already got it. Get into the

00:03:21.519 --> 00:03:22.630
prayer

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:26.070
vein of believing that you've received

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:30.110
it before you've got it, and

00:03:30.110 --> 00:03:30.120
stay

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.550
in the atmosphere of saying, 'Thank you,

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:34.949
Father. I just believe I'm going to

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:36.910
receive.'I'm

00:03:36.920 --> 00:03:38.670
not going to take

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:41.830
the care of 'I've got to have this right

00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:45.990
now.'I

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.750
thought this was interesting also in

00:03:50.750 --> 00:03:50.760
1

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:52.550
Peter

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:56.270
3:7: 'Husbands, likewise, dwell with them

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:58.710
with understanding, giving honor to the

00:03:58.720 --> 00:04:01.229
wife as to the weaker vessel and as

00:04:01.239 --> 00:04:03.030
being heirs together of the grace of

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:04.589
life, that your prayers may not be

00:04:04.589 --> 00:04:04.599
hindered.'So

00:04:04.599 --> 00:04:06.710
he's saying if you're not

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:07.990
honoring your wife and you're not

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:11.309
treating her right, your prayers will be

00:04:11.319 --> 00:04:14.270
hindered.

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:21.069
1

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:31.029
Peter 3:7 states

00:04:31.039 --> 00:04:33.150
that if we don't honor our wives and

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:35.110
treat them right, your prayers

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:36.150
aren't going to be heard; they're going

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:38.510
to be

00:04:38.510 --> 00:04:38.520
hindered.

00:04:38.520 --> 00:04:42.670
There is a flow of honoring

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:45.830
your spouse. Wife, honor your husband

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:48.270
too, but there is a flow as the head of

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:50.469
the house. If you are treating your wife

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:51.469
like

00:04:51.479 --> 00:04:53.909
trash and you're

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:03.110
just a bully,

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:05.830
your

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:08.029
prayers will be

00:05:08.039 --> 00:05:11.029
hindered. Those scriptures

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:12.990
pop out and make

00:05:12.990 --> 00:05:13.000
you realize

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:18.029
it's all an equilibrium.

00:05:18.039 --> 00:05:21.670
The spirit

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:25.029
realm is alive, and to get

00:05:25.039 --> 00:05:27.909
things active like an engine,

00:05:27.919 --> 00:05:29.870
you've

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:31.469
got all the pistons

00:05:31.479 --> 00:05:33.629
firing, the fan belt,

00:05:33.639 --> 00:05:36.230
all of it going. But if one

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:39.390
thing is off, that car

00:05:39.400 --> 00:05:42.469
won't go very far. When you put

00:05:42.479 --> 00:05:45.790
your prayer and you get all the things

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.950
in motion like

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:49.990
that engine, that

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.909
car has the ability to go really fast.

00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:58.629
But if it's off just even by a

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.390
little bit,

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:02.870
the whole thing is off-kilter. If you get the

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:04.870
timing belt

00:06:04.870 --> 00:06:04.880
wrong,

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:06.270
you're going to throw a rod; it's

00:06:06.280 --> 00:06:08.589
over.

00:06:08.599 --> 00:06:09.950
I'm trying to

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:13.110
compare prayer and walking by faith

00:06:13.110 --> 00:06:13.120
to

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:16.550
an engine. How do you make the engine in

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:19.550
the spirit realm run at 100 miles per hour

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:21.390
so that we're doing it full force and

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:23.749
not having these

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:25.710
delayed

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:28.070
responses?

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:33.950
Faith

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:37.150
works by love. If you're not walking

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:39.550
in love, you're not going to get your

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:40.510
blessing.

00:06:50.280 --> 00:06:52.110
Love takes no account of

00:06:52.110 --> 00:06:52.120
a

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:53.950
suffered wrong. When people talk

00:06:53.950 --> 00:06:53.960
bad

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:56.589
about you on the internet, I take no

00:06:56.599 --> 00:06:57.990
account of suffering wrong. There

00:06:57.990 --> 00:06:58.000
are

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:00.309
plenty of times I could do it every day,

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:03.029
and I go, 'Oh God, help me, Father,

00:07:03.039 --> 00:07:05.350
to take no account of a suffered

00:07:05.350 --> 00:07:05.360
wrong.'These

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.029
people are

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:11.110
running me down on Twitter, on X,

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:13.550
and saying all sorts of things. Love takes no

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:16.070
account of a suffered wrong. Help me

00:07:16.080 --> 00:07:18.869
to come up higher in my love walk

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:21.029
because the Bible

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:24.510
says that faith works by

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:28.830
love. God is love,

00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:32.029
and perfect love casteth out all fear

00:07:32.039 --> 00:07:34.430
because fear has torment, and fear

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:37.230
tolerated is faith contaminated. All

00:07:37.240 --> 00:07:39.469
these things are an

00:07:39.479 --> 00:07:42.430
equilibrium. Getting

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:44.629
it in motion so that

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:50.149
the prayer engine

00:07:50.149 --> 00:07:50.159
works.

00:07:50.159 --> 00:07:52.110
How do we make this

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:55.830
prayer engine work? More praise, more

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:58.550
thanksgiving, more glory to God, more

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:01.390
honoring him, lifting up holy hands,

00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:02.869
and

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:06.189
keeping your heart right.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:24.589
I

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:26.469
want impartation from the Holy Spirit

00:08:26.479 --> 00:08:28.589
every day, and I want to be changed from

00:08:28.599 --> 00:08:30.189
glory to glory every

00:08:30.199 --> 00:08:33.670
day.

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:36.670
I don't want to keep going down the

00:08:36.680 --> 00:08:38.870
highway the wrong

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.670
way

00:08:40.680 --> 00:08:43.389
and

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:45.949
wasting time day

00:08:45.959 --> 00:08:48.070
after day.

00:08:48.070 --> 00:08:48.080
If

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:49.829
nothing is changing, it's because it's

00:08:49.839 --> 00:08:51.110
off-kilter.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:53.790
You're going, 'Lord, what's broken in

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:55.750
this

00:08:55.750 --> 00:08:55.760
engine?'If

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:58.150
I can

00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:00.509
help you with one thing

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:02.710
through these videos

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:05.230
and you grab one

00:09:05.240 --> 00:09:08.110
little thing that changes

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:10.190
your life forever, then we've done our

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:13.710
job. I want to help you get

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:15.630
higher in your prayer.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.269
When the care of life tries to choke you

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:27.470
out, that's one

00:09:27.480 --> 00:09:30.269
of the big ones.

00:09:30.279 --> 00:09:34.150
I try so hard not to pray the care

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:36.430
because

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:40.389
begging is not believing. Get your care

00:09:40.399 --> 00:09:41.550
out of your

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:45.269
prayer. Yes, get your care out of

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:48.470
your prayer.

00:09:57.519 --> 00:10:00.910
God is not moved by your

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:04.590
need; he's moved by your faith.

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:08.269
Without faith, it is impossible to

00:10:08.279 --> 00:10:09.269
please

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:12.150
him. For he that cometh to God must

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:16.470
believe that he is and that he is a

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:20.150
