00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:24.230
him.

00:10:33.430 --> 00:10:33.440
I

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:47.470
pray that you all

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:50.629
get a little something and

00:10:50.639 --> 00:10:53.389
add that to your engine.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:00.590
Instead of

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.069
going down the same road expecting

00:11:03.079 --> 00:11:05.269
different results and

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:10.269
going, 'Why is my life so messed

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:13.870
up?'You

00:11:16.079 --> 00:11:18.710
learn by

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:20.430
trial and error,

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:21.910
and by listening to Brother

00:11:21.910 --> 00:11:21.920
Hagin,

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:24.590
you go through life's

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:28.430
emotions and

00:11:28.430 --> 00:11:28.440
say,

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.470
'Holy Spirit, I can't do this

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:33.550
without

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:37.030
you.'He

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.949
corrects those he loves.

00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:45.949
I told Diana, 'Do I

00:11:45.959 --> 00:11:50.230
get a lot

00:11:50.230 --> 00:11:50.240
right?'because

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:52.590
I feel I'm always being

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:55.550
molded and corrected.

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:03.790
I want to just be on the right road

