00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:08.430
You can't

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:10.829
put a square tire on a car and

00:12:10.839 --> 00:12:12.949
expect it to run, Brandon.

00:12:12.949 --> 00:12:12.959
You've

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:17.230
got

00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:19.110
to put a round tire on there.

00:12:27.199 --> 00:12:29.710
I walk away, and

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:32.030
it happens a lot. Even to

00:12:32.030 --> 00:12:32.040
Brandon,

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:34.069
I'll give

00:12:34.069 --> 00:12:34.079
him

00:12:34.079 --> 00:12:36.550
a tidbit so he

00:12:36.550 --> 00:12:36.560
doesn't

00:12:36.560 --> 00:12:37.949
