00:12:37.959 --> 00:12:41.629
older.

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:48.269
Learn it now,

00:12:48.269 --> 00:12:48.279
Brandon,

00:12:48.279 --> 00:12:50.710
so when you get

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:51.949
to

00:12:51.959 --> 00:12:54.389
my age, you're

00:12:54.399 --> 00:12:57.350
