00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:15.590
I was talking

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:18.870
about how we bring prayer to a

00:13:18.880 --> 00:13:21.310
different

00:13:21.310 --> 00:13:21.320
level—it's

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:24.430
