00:13:29.399 --> 00:13:31.750
thank you for what you're about to

00:13:34.870 --> 00:13:34.880
do.'May

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:42.189
is almost here; I'm

00:13:42.199 --> 00:13:45.990
going to anticipate something huge in

