00:14:37.000 --> 00:14:40.790
I expect God to talk to

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:43.629
me whenever I'm

00:14:43.639 --> 00:14:47.509
praying.

00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:50.389
I said something; he's going to

00:14:50.399 --> 00:14:53.509
say something. He wants to lead and guide

00:14:53.519 --> 00:14:56.389
me.

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:58.030
There

00:14:59.509 --> 00:14:59.519
are

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.670
some things he tells us

00:15:03.670 --> 00:15:03.680
that

